WEBVTT

00:01.683 --> 00:03.710
Hank, I want to apply to medical school.

00:03.734 --> 00:05.769
It's the admissions office
from Johns Hopkins.

00:05.803 --> 00:07.038
I'm wait-listed.

00:07.071 --> 00:08.039
Is it true?

00:08.071 --> 00:09.372
Doctor called this afternoon

00:09.406 --> 00:10.675
and if all goes well,

00:10.708 --> 00:13.276
we could be pregnant by
the end of the month.

00:13.310 --> 00:15.179
Hello, Ms. Green.

00:15.211 --> 00:17.113
I'm Dr. Sacani from HankMed.

00:17.147 --> 00:18.415
Is this you being nice,

00:18.449 --> 00:21.218
or you wanting to know
what happens in book six?

00:21.252 --> 00:23.487
Um, both.

00:23.520 --> 00:25.656
I got big news. I'm getting married!

00:25.688 --> 00:27.123
That's a little sudden, no?

00:27.156 --> 00:29.893
You know, Hank, your
father blames himself

00:29.927 --> 00:31.295
for all of your relationship problems.

00:31.328 --> 00:32.630
What do you mean?

00:32.662 --> 00:34.098
He's afraid you've become more like him

00:34.130 --> 00:36.433
and he thinks that's why you
can't seem to settle down.

00:36.466 --> 00:38.969
I had a major dishonesty relapse.

00:39.002 --> 00:40.270
But it won't happen again, right?

00:40.304 --> 00:41.471
Never.

00:41.505 --> 00:42.907
Paige and I will come to your wedding,

00:42.940 --> 00:45.509
but make no mistake,

00:45.542 --> 00:47.310
my first job as a parent

00:47.343 --> 00:50.615
will be protecting my family from you.

00:52.349 --> 00:54.318
<i>♪ Close your eyes ♪</i>

00:54.350 --> 00:57.387
<i>♪ Your mommy's here beside you ♪</i>

00:57.420 --> 01:02.359
<i>♪ Feel my love and let
my spirit guide you ♪</i>

01:02.392 --> 01:04.861
<i>♪ I'll stay with you ♪</i>

01:04.894 --> 01:09.099
<i>♪ Until you fall asleep ♪</i>

01:09.132 --> 01:11.835
<i>♪ My dear ♪</i>

01:11.868 --> 01:17.141
<i>♪ 'Cause I will never
leave you or desert you ♪</i>

01:17.174 --> 01:22.813
<i>♪ And I will do my best
to never hurt you ♪</i>

01:22.846 --> 01:25.148
♪ But if I do ♪

01:25.182 --> 01:30.087
♪ Please know it always breaks ♪

01:30.120 --> 01:33.124
♪ My heart ♪

01:33.156 --> 01:38.695
♪ So as I watch you
dreaming something new ♪

01:38.728 --> 01:44.067
♪ Know that you're the proof
that dreams come true ♪

01:44.100 --> 01:49.540
♪ Because of the girl you are ♪

01:49.573 --> 01:54.745
♪ And the sister I know you'll be ♪

01:54.778 --> 01:57.882
♪ So good night ♪

01:57.915 --> 02:04.621
♪ God bless this family ♪

02:04.654 --> 02:06.757
I can't believe we finally
find out tomorrow.

02:06.790 --> 02:08.893
- I know.
- God.

02:08.925 --> 02:10.494
I'm trying not to be nervous.

02:10.526 --> 02:12.129
- Do I seem nervous?
- A little.

02:12.161 --> 02:13.863
Yeah, I'll try harder.

02:13.897 --> 02:16.034
Slow. Click, click.

02:17.468 --> 02:18.869
I will have you know

02:18.901 --> 02:21.105
that we were rehearsing this
dance for Newberg, not Dad.

02:21.137 --> 02:22.906
So don't think I'm forgiving him, okay?

02:22.940 --> 02:24.141
Okay.

02:24.173 --> 02:26.776
Actually, since you're flying solo,

02:26.809 --> 02:28.445
do you want to borrow
my wife to practice?

02:28.478 --> 02:30.414
- Thank you, honey...
- Oh...

02:30.446 --> 02:31.848
But I'm happy to help.

02:31.881 --> 02:34.584
Ms. Newberg expects you out on
the dance floor too, you know.

02:34.618 --> 02:36.387
Yeah, thank you, but maybe another time.

02:36.420 --> 02:37.887
Sure.

02:37.921 --> 02:40.291
Um, oh, if it's okay,
I'd like your plus one.

02:40.323 --> 02:41.926
The wedding's become a hot
ticket all of a sudden

02:41.958 --> 02:43.526
and the administrator over
at Riverhead Hospital

02:43.559 --> 02:44.527
really wants to go.

02:44.560 --> 02:45.563
Yeah, it's not okay.

02:45.595 --> 02:47.230
Okay, babe, we got a lot of work to do.

02:47.263 --> 02:49.933
Okay. Excuse me.

02:49.966 --> 02:52.069
I take it the staff
meeting isn't happening.

02:52.101 --> 02:54.637
Uh, no, and do you mind being
on call for a few hours?

02:54.671 --> 02:56.307
We've got an important
wedding commitment

02:56.339 --> 02:57.307
and we don't wanna be late for it.

02:57.340 --> 02:58.808
Okay, just five more minutes.

03:05.149 --> 03:06.317
Oh, my God.

03:06.350 --> 03:07.317
I can't believe we're about to meet

03:07.351 --> 03:08.752
<i>the</i> Annette Bellamy.

03:08.786 --> 03:10.821
I grew up watching her movies, okay?

03:10.853 --> 03:13.224
And my parents took me to see
her on Broadway three times.

03:13.256 --> 03:15.291
Can you try to stand
as still as possible?

03:15.325 --> 03:16.393
Oh, my bad.

03:16.427 --> 03:18.796
Maybe, Paige, you should
gush a little less

03:18.828 --> 03:21.332
when she gets here,
for both their sakes.

03:21.364 --> 03:23.868
Oh, that's all right.
Annette is used to it.

03:23.900 --> 03:26.002
That's what you get when
you're a living legend.

03:29.373 --> 03:34.111
- What a dump.
- Darling!

03:37.013 --> 03:39.149
Annette, this is Divya.

03:39.183 --> 03:41.986
And Paige, the peppy
girl married to Evan

03:42.018 --> 03:44.522
and the PA, you told me.

03:44.554 --> 03:46.756
Oh, my God. I just, like...

03:46.790 --> 03:48.559
Oh, my God, it's...

03:48.591 --> 03:49.726
it's like you.

03:49.760 --> 03:50.960
It's like you. It's like you right here.

03:50.994 --> 03:52.229
Like...

03:52.262 --> 03:53.764
I've watched you in every
movie you have ever made.

03:53.797 --> 03:56.867
I used to pretend that I was
you in "Hold Me Closer."

03:56.899 --> 03:59.269
Why'd you stop?

03:59.303 --> 04:01.338
Uh...

04:01.370 --> 04:02.505
Sh... Uh...

04:02.539 --> 04:04.674
Relax. I'm messing with you.

04:04.708 --> 04:05.676
Oh.

04:05.708 --> 04:06.709
But I'll tell you one thing,

04:06.743 --> 04:09.313
it was this woman...

04:09.345 --> 04:12.215
she's the one who has the real talent.

04:12.249 --> 04:14.984
If she hadn't made a career
out of getting married,

04:15.018 --> 04:17.688
she could have been a
bigger star than I am.

04:17.721 --> 04:20.357
Oh, Ms. Newberg, you acted?

04:20.389 --> 04:22.625
- I dabbled.
- Ha.

04:22.659 --> 04:25.396
She had presence. She had poise.

04:25.428 --> 04:26.964
She had balls.

04:26.997 --> 04:28.799
How's the new show?

04:28.832 --> 04:31.101
Time of my life.

04:31.134 --> 04:35.706
Cumberbatch gets a little
handsy now and then.

04:35.738 --> 04:37.140
Annette just flew in from London

04:37.173 --> 04:38.909
where she's working on
a new musical version

04:38.942 --> 04:40.244
of "Uncle Vanya."

04:40.276 --> 04:41.411
Oh.

04:41.445 --> 04:45.149
I am so happy you are here.

04:45.181 --> 04:46.616
I couldn't do this without you.

04:46.649 --> 04:48.486
Clearly.

04:48.519 --> 04:50.554
I've been to all five of her weddings.

04:50.587 --> 04:52.589
Well, this is my last one.

04:52.623 --> 04:55.192
Eddie is the only man I ever loved...

04:55.224 --> 04:56.526
for more than a year.

04:56.560 --> 04:59.363
Wait till you see me in my new dress.

04:59.396 --> 05:01.866
Oh, I sizzle.

05:01.899 --> 05:04.635
I think this is my
Schmoopy's way of telling me

05:04.668 --> 05:06.036
to lay off the Oreos.

05:06.068 --> 05:07.203
Maybe.

05:07.236 --> 05:09.939
Hey, Evan, could you give
your dad a hand here?

05:09.973 --> 05:11.242
I think you can handle it.

05:11.274 --> 05:12.442
No, no, no, I... I...

05:12.476 --> 05:14.043
you know what it... it's the wrong size.

05:14.077 --> 05:15.411
I can't figure this out.

05:15.445 --> 05:17.348
Uh, Dad, cumberbunds are adjustable.

05:17.380 --> 05:20.049
Yeah. Hank, would you do me a favor?

05:20.082 --> 05:22.986
Go and see what Ms. Newberg says.

05:23.019 --> 05:25.022
You know, I-I would like to,

05:25.055 --> 05:27.224
but I can't see her in her
dress before the wedding.

05:27.257 --> 05:28.358
Really?

05:28.392 --> 05:30.627
Well, cumberbunds are
so important to her.

05:30.661 --> 05:32.663
Oh, yeah. Okay.

05:37.567 --> 05:38.769
I'm gonna go with him.

05:42.438 --> 05:44.407
- Divya.
- Yes?

05:44.440 --> 05:46.543
I hear you're going to medical school.

05:46.577 --> 05:47.877
Uh, yes.

05:47.911 --> 05:49.446
I just don't know where yet.

05:49.478 --> 05:52.649
And Paige, you're trying
to get knocked up?

05:52.683 --> 05:55.052
Wow.

05:55.084 --> 05:56.954
Ms. Newberg really did fill you in.

05:56.986 --> 06:00.490
All right, girls,
fasten your seat belts.

06:05.062 --> 06:09.433
♪ I'm not one who suffers
from false modesty ♪

06:09.466 --> 06:10.601
♪ So I'll crow ♪

06:10.634 --> 06:13.370
♪ I'm looking, oh, so goddessy ♪

06:13.402 --> 06:15.738
♪ I hope it doesn't cause you any harm ♪

06:15.772 --> 06:17.908
♪ Or set off an alarm ♪

06:17.940 --> 06:20.143
♪ Sixth time's the charm ♪

06:23.313 --> 06:26.483
♪ Doing things the easy
way is not for me ♪

06:26.515 --> 06:28.051
♪ Sad but true ♪

06:28.084 --> 06:31.721
♪ My eggs don't seem to care
that Evan's hot for me ♪

06:31.755 --> 06:34.024
♪ Screw you, low motility ♪

06:34.056 --> 06:36.159
♪ Eff you, infertility ♪

06:36.192 --> 06:38.796
♪ I'm makin' a baby ♪

06:38.829 --> 06:40.264
♪ Four kids and med school ♪

06:40.296 --> 06:43.499
♪ They thought I couldn't do it ♪

06:43.533 --> 06:48.038
♪ But I'm the queen of "Hey,
there's nothing to it" ♪

06:48.070 --> 06:49.839
♪ So screw it ♪

06:49.873 --> 06:52.041
♪ It's so much more than chemistry ♪

06:52.075 --> 06:54.211
♪ I'm ready for my pregnancy ♪

06:54.243 --> 06:56.512
♪ Johns Hopkins, you're accepting me ♪

06:56.546 --> 06:58.849
♪ There's no question,
it's my destiny ♪

06:58.882 --> 07:00.985
♪ And now the moment
I've been waiting for ♪

07:01.017 --> 07:03.620
♪ Is ready to begin ♪

07:03.654 --> 07:05.289
♪ So you better open up that door ♪

07:05.322 --> 07:07.458
♪ Or I'm kicking it in ♪

07:11.094 --> 07:12.195
Hey.

07:12.228 --> 07:13.496
Hi.

07:13.529 --> 07:18.067
♪ How's it going? ♪

07:18.101 --> 07:20.269
♪ We're doing just fine ♪

07:20.303 --> 07:22.673
♪ Yes, I'd say that we're fine ♪

07:22.705 --> 07:26.809
♪ I had a question ♪

07:26.842 --> 07:29.178
♪ That I cannot seem to recall ♪

07:29.212 --> 07:31.481
♪ Dad's cumberbund is too small ♪

07:31.514 --> 07:33.851
♪ Tell him, please, no cumberbund ♪

07:33.884 --> 07:34.985
♪ Straps are fine ♪

07:35.017 --> 07:37.421
♪ In fact, they are preferred ♪

07:37.454 --> 07:38.422
♪ Got it ♪

07:38.454 --> 07:39.589
♪ Preferred ♪

07:39.623 --> 07:40.658
♪ We heard ♪

07:45.127 --> 07:47.330
♪ I'm finally the star ♪

07:47.363 --> 07:50.000
♪ Of the show ♪

07:50.033 --> 07:52.202
♪ I'm ready for my close-up ♪

07:52.235 --> 07:53.437
♪ Here I go ♪

07:53.469 --> 07:54.438
♪ Here I go ♪

07:54.471 --> 07:56.305
♪ Here I go ♪

07:56.339 --> 07:58.709
♪ 'Cause all I need is Eddie for me ♪

07:58.741 --> 08:00.943
♪ Johns Hopkins, are you ready for me? ♪

08:00.976 --> 08:03.046
♪ I put the "Mmm" in maternity ♪

08:03.079 --> 08:05.582
♪ There's no question,
it's my destiny ♪

08:05.615 --> 08:07.885
♪ 'Cause now the moment
I've been waiting for ♪

08:07.918 --> 08:10.120
♪ Is ready to begin ♪

08:10.152 --> 08:12.488
♪ And I'm not waiting anymore ♪

08:12.522 --> 08:15.392
♪ So you better open up that door ♪

08:15.425 --> 08:17.795
♪ Before I ♪

08:17.827 --> 08:20.130
♪ Kick ♪

08:20.163 --> 08:22.299
♪ It ♪

08:22.332 --> 08:26.337
♪ In ♪

08:31.374 --> 08:34.378
Annette, honey, are you okay?

08:35.378 --> 08:38.716
It's just jet lag.

