formed blood vessels

40:40.449 --> 40:41.583
bleeding in your brain.

40:41.616 --> 40:44.219
Is that why I've been
having hallucinations?

40:44.252 --> 40:46.323
Yes, and you developed epilepsy

40:46.355 --> 40:48.123
caused by the presence
of the malformation,

40:48.156 --> 40:51.527
but the surgery will evacuate
the bleeding and remove it.

40:51.560 --> 40:55.531
I'm sorry to say, you will lose
your musical hallucinations,

40:55.565 --> 40:57.500
but the good news is

40:57.533 --> 41:00.636
