face of all medical wisdom,

42:53.549 --> 42:55.418
break a leg.

42:55.451 --> 42:56.453
Okay.

43:10.366 --> 43:11.400
We're gonna stay in touch,

43:11.433 --> 43:13.236
we're gonna text, we'll email,

43:13.268 --> 43:14.236
we'll Facebook.

43:14.270 --> 43:15.237
We're gonna send a pigeon.

43:15.270 --> 43:16.238
Oh.

43:16.272 --> 43:17.239
And when we come back,

43:17.272 --> 43:18.707
we're gonna have a party.

43:18.741 --> 43:20.443
- Come on. Let's go.
- We're going!

43:20.475 --> 43:22.511
- Good-bye! We love you.
- Bye, Dad.

43:22.545 --> 43:23.713
Have fun.

43:30.252 --> 43:32.754
Well, that's stating the obvious.

43:32.788 --> 43:33.823
Yeah.

43:33.854 --> 43:35.224
You're on deck, Henry, officially now.

43:35.256 --> 43:37.024
Hey, guess what? Big surprise, babe.

43:37.058 --> 43:40.863
We got to find Hank a bride. Oh.

43:40.897 --> 43:43.399
You're not actually letting
Evan's teasing get to you?

43:43.431 --> 43:45.234
No. No.

43:45.268 --> 43:48.771
I'm gonna miss it.

43:48.803 --> 43:49.872
Am I going somewhere?

43:49.905 --> 43:51.640
Everyone seems to be.

43:51.674 --> 43:53.309
I mean, this one's going
to medical school,

43:53.341 --> 43:55.511
somewhere, you're running the hospital,

43:55.545 --> 43:59.749
Jeremiah's opening up
a lab and his heart.

43:59.781 --> 44:02.150
Maybe it's time for me
to make a change too.

44:02.183 --> 44:04.419
What kind of change?

44:04.453 --> 44:07.357
I don't know. A big one.

44:08.658 --> 44:11.594
Maybe as big as the one
that brought me out here.

44:27.542 --> 44:29.378
Okay. Thanks.

44:29.411 --> 44:32.147
What's going on? Who was that?

44:32.181 --> 44:36.486
What is it? You okay?

44:36.518 --> 44:38.754
Babe.

44:38.788 --> 44:41.291
I'm pregnant.

44:42.457 --> 44:43.660
What do you...

44:43.691 --> 44:46.027
The blood test came back positive.

44:46.062 --> 44:48.264
It's more accurate.

44:48.297 --> 44:52.535
That's why they tell you
not to cheat at home.

44:52.567 --> 44:54.336
We're pregnant.

44:57.940 --> 45:00.310
Oh, my God.

45:05.681 --> 45:07.250
Let's keep it between us.

45:07.283 --> 45:10.053
I just... I want one night
of just us knowing.

45:10.085 --> 45:11.321
Oh, yeah. Okay. Whatever you want...

45:11.352 --> 45:12.454
We're pregnant!

45:12.487 --> 45:13.589
What?

45:13.623 --> 45:15.458
- We're pregnant!
- Congratulations!

45:15.491 --> 45:17.826
Oh, my God! So exciting.

45:17.858 --> 45:19.293
Paige!

45:19.328 --> 45:20.830
Oh, my God.

